 center;" align="center">                                    <span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Calibri, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">The 2018 People’s Choice Awards, airing for the first time on E! Sunday, November 11, includes a much more diverse array of cable nominees. As a result, the show offers clients a chance to connect with a broad and enthusiastic audience. Use the action button to follow us on Twitter for live coverage of the event.</span>                                   </div>                                   </div>                                 </div> </td>                                </tr>                               </tbody>                              </table>                             </div> </td>                           </tr>                          </tbody>                         </table>                         <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" class="galileo-ap-layout-editor" style="min-width: 100%;">                          <tbody>                           <tr>                            <td class=" editor-col OneColumnMobile" width="100%" align="" valign="top" style="background-color: rgb(19, 151, 183);" bgcolor="1397B7">                             <div class="gl-contains-spacer">                              <table class="editor-spacer" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">                               <tbody>                                <tr>                                 <td class="" align="center" valign="top">                                  <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%">                                   <tbody>                                    <tr>                                     <td class="spacer-base" width="100%" align="center" valign="top" style="padding-bottom: 10px; height: 1px; line-height: 1px;">                                      <div>                 